textBeforeTable: Conferences Ranked by Winning Percentage (everyone plays everyone 100 times) WhatIfSports.com utilizes the results of the weekly college football power rankings to rank all 12 DI FBS conferences, including the independents. Conferences are ordered by winning percentage against other conferences in the over 700,000 simulated games. For more inforamtion, check out this week's college football power rankings.
